issue_summary: [Team Loyalty] Loyalty banner on location view
issue_description:
WHat: We need to add a loyalty banner to thee site where all properties from certain chain are available.
 Additionally, once a user registers or logs in, their status should be preserved as they browse different properties and enter the booking engineExample of such URL:   with additional
parameter   Why:
Promote Loyalty: By prominently displaying the loyalty banner, we aim to increase awareness and participation in our loyalty program, encouraging more users to take advantage of its benefits.Enhance user experience: seamless loyalty registration or log in improve the user experience, making it easier for users to book and engage with our services, ultimately driving customer satisfaction and loyalty. If login/ registered process is not finished on master / location view - after clicking on selected child - banner should be in status enabling login and register again - and user needs to start this process again. FIGMA: https://www.figma.com/design/8ueAWE3EfRt7muTko0SD4H/Loyalty?node-id=5407-9172&node-type=canvas&t=eDDTNKnRdRA3Zpnb-0
